      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total dream! This car has been my baby\u2014garage-kept, pampered, and kept in truly flawless condition. It honestly feels like you're driving it right off the showroom floor for the very first time. If you've been looking for that perfect, like-new ride without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it! I\u2019m so excited for someone else to get behind the wheel and enjoy it as much as I have. Shoot me a message if you want to come take a look!",
