    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional FD3S chassis featuring the sequential twin-turbocharged 13B-REW rotary engine. This specimen maintains factory-spec boost pressure and exhibits flawless compression across both rotors. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise five-speed short-throw gearbox and a Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque transfer. Suspension geometry is preserved via original double-wishbones with refreshed bushings, providing the telepathic turn-in characteristic of the front-midship layout. The vacuum rack has been meticulously overhauled, and the cooling system upgraded for thermal efficiency without compromising the OEM aesthetic. A turn-key collector-grade example with a documented service history and zero structural oxidation.",
      "price": 48500.0,
