    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality specimen that satisfies even the most discerning collector's standards. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, and its condition reflects a 'no-expense-spared' ownership philosophy. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory-original luster with zero swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections, thanks to a professional-grade ceramic coating. Every body panel is laser-straight with perfect alignment. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, the dashboard is free of any UV fading, and the original carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since day one. All technological features, including the infotainment system and driver-assist sensors, operate with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a full service history with all scheduled maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians. The engine bay is detailed to a mirror finish, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean, showing no signs of inclement weather exposure. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks, smells, and drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership floor.",
